<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3321400" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">其实不难，虚化背景，突出重点人物；光线柔和，暖色调；五官略作调整即可。原图——<br><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/2c565081e6175a76d40e7563743559e8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="398" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/2c565081e6175a76d40e7563743559e8_r.jpg">PS后——<br><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/bf1b0b0c6cbec0578e6eaedd291e86eb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="327" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/bf1b0b0c6cbec0578e6eaedd291e86eb_r.jpg">
